#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:appointment.type,message_intro:environmental_agency.appointment_type_3
msgid ""
"Is your fleet <strong>costing you more than it should</strong> in fuel and "
"emissions? Let’s change that! In our <strong>Fleet Emissions Planning "
"Meeting</strong>, we’ll explore strategies to <strong>reduce fuel costs, "
"lower carbon emissions, and transition to greener alternatives</strong>—all "
"while keeping your operations running smoothly. Whether you’re looking to "
"<strong>optimize routes, integrate EVs, or earn sustainability "
"certifications</strong>, our expert team will craft a <strong>practical, "
"cost-effective roadmap</strong> for your fleet. Sustainability isn’t just "
"good for the planet—it’s a smart business move. <strong>Book your free "
"consultation today and start driving toward a cleaner future!</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Bruger din flåde for meget</strong> brændstof og udleder for mange "
"emissioner? Det kan vi ændre! I vores <strong>møde om planlægning af "
"flådeemissioner</strong> vil vi gennemgå strategier til at <strong>reducere "
"brændstofomkostninger, mindske CO₂-udledning og skifte til mere miljøvenlige "
"alternativer</strong> – alt sammen uden at forstyrre din virksomheds drift. "
"Uanset om du vil <strong>optimere ruter, integrere elbiler eller opnå "
"bæredygtighedscertificeringer</strong>, udarbejder vores ekspertteam en "
"<strong>praktisk og omkostningseffektiv strategisk plan</strong> for din "
"flåde. Bæredygtighed er ikke kun godt for planeten – det er også en klog "
"forretningsbeslutning. <strong>Book din gratis konsultation i dag og tag "
"skridtet mod en renere fremtid!</strong>"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid "Let's get started to see the change you want to see in the world! 🌍"
msgstr "Lad os skabe den forandring, du vil se i verden! 🌍"

