msgstr ""
"Knyt tidsregistreringer til fakturaer i <strong>Salgsappen</strong>, generér "
"fakturaen baseret på den registrerede tid, og send den til kunden."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Log meetings, calls, and emails directly in the CRM. Use the pipeline "
"to<strong> track the progress of each lead</strong> (e.g., New → Internal "
"Analysis → Qualified → Proposal → Won)."
msgstr ""
"Registrer møder, opkald og e-mails direkte i CRM-systemet. Brug pipelinen "
"til at<strong> følge fremskridtet for hver lead</strong> (f.eks. Ny → Intern "
"analyse → Kvalificeret → Forslag → Vundet)."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage consulting fees, track project expenses, and generate financial "
"reports using the <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, "
"103);\">Accounting App</font></strong> for seamless financial management."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\""
">Bogføringsappen</font></strong> til at administrere konsulenthonorarer, "
"spore projektudgifter og generere finansielle rapporter for nem "
"økonomistyring."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid "Manually add a new line to register time on specific tasks if needed."
msgstr "Tilføj en ny linje manuelt for at registrere tiden på udvalgte opgaver."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid "Measure the impact of each project and prioritize effectively. 🌳"
msgstr "Mål projektets effekt, og prioritér opgaverne effektivt. 🌳"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3085
msgid "My Company"
msgstr "Min virksomhed"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model:crm.stage,name:environmental_agency.crm_stage_6
msgid "Not enough climate impact"
msgstr "Utilstrækkelig klimapåvirkning"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone into"
" a tool to manage your entire workflow."
msgstr ""
"Odoo er fuldt integreret i én app. Download den, og forvandl din telefon til "
"et værktøj, hvormed du kan styre hele din virksomhed."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo offers endless customization possibilities for your environmental "
"agency:"
msgstr "Odoo giver dit miljøagentur uendelige tilpasningsmuligheder:"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"Oversigten viser naturligvis kun de funktioner, der følger med pakken. Du "
"kan tilføje nye apps, redigere eller slette demodata og prøve dig frem!"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once a lead shows interest, generate a <strong>quotation in the Sales "
"App</strong> offering services like strategy consulting, carbon footprint "
"assessments, or ESG reporting."
msgstr ""
"Så snart en kunde viser interesse, opretter du et <strong>tilbud i "
"Salgsappen</strong> og tilbyder tjenester som strategirådgivning, CO₂-"
"fodaftryksvurderinger eller ESG-rapportering."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid "Ongoing Support"
msgstr "Løbende support"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>Appointment App</strong> and configure available slots for "
"demos."
msgstr ""
"Åbn <strong>Aftalerappen</strong>, og konfigurér ledige tidsvinduer til "
"demoer."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>CRM App</strong>, create a new lead for an organization "
"interested in sustainability services, and assign the lead to a team member."
msgstr ""
"Åbn <strong>CRM-appen</strong>, opret en ny lead for en organisation, der er "
"interesseret i bæredygtighedstjenester, og tildel leadet til et teammedlem."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the <strong>Timesheet app.</strong>"
msgstr "Åbn <strong>Tidsregistreringsappen.</strong>"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organize sustainability workshops, conferences, and training sessions "
"through the <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Event "
"App</font></strong> to raise awareness and promote environmental "
"initiatives."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\""
">Arrangementerappen</font></strong> til at organisere "
"bæredygtighedsworkshops, konferencer og kurser og fremme miljøinitiativer."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organize tasks by Milestones and assign specific dates to key stages in the "
"case."
msgstr ""
"Organisér opgaver efter milepæle, og sæt specifikke datoer på de vigtigste "
"faser."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid ""
"Our commitment to the environment includes using eco-friendly materials in "
"our products and services, ensuring minimal impact on the planet while "
"maintaining high quality."
msgstr ""
"Vores engagement for miljøet omfatter også brugen af bæredygtige materialer "
"i vores produkter og tjenester for at minimere påvirkningen på planeten, "
"samtidig med at vi sikrer høj kvalitet."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid ""
"Our team provides continuous assistance and expertise, ensuring you receive "
"guidance and support throughout your environmental initiatives."
msgstr ""
"Vores team står klar med løbende vejledning og ekspertise, så du trygt kan "
"gennemføre dine miljøinitiativer."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model:sale.order.template.line,name:environmental_agency.sale_order_template_line_3
msgid ""
"Please note that these amounts are indicative and that the actual time spent"
" will be strictly monitored, reported and invoiced if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Bemærk, at disse beløb kun er vejledende, og at den faktiske anvendte tid "
"nøje overvåges, rapporteres og eventuelt faktureres."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model:project.project.stage,name:environmental_agency.project_project_stage_5
msgid "Project Templates"
msgstr "Projektskabeloner"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model:product.template,name:environmental_agency.product_product_3_product_template
#: model:project.project,name:environmental_agency.project_project_3
msgid "Prospective Studies"
msgstr "Prospektive studier"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:appointment.type,message_intro:environmental_agency.appointment_type_2
msgid ""
"Ready to make your business greener, more efficient, and future-proof? Book "
"a <strong>Discovery Call</strong> with our expert environmental agency! We "
"help businesses <strong>cut costs, reduce waste, and achieve sustainability "
"goals</strong>—whether it’s going <strong>carbon neutral, minimizing plastic"
" use, or earning eco certifications</strong>. Consumers and regulators are "
"demanding greener operations—<strong>stay ahead of the curve</strong> while "
"improving your brand image and bottom line. Our tailored strategies make "
"sustainability <strong>simple, practical, and profitable</strong>. Let’s "
"explore how we can help your business thrive while protecting the planet."
msgstr ""
"Er du klar til at gøre din virksomhed grønnere, mere effektiv og "
"fremtidssikret? Book en <strong>første samtale</strong> med vores erfarne "
"rådgivere inden for miljøbeskyttelse! Vi hjælper virksomheder med at <strong>"
"sænke omkostningerne, reducere affaldet og nå bæredygtighedsmålene</strong> "
"– hvad enten det er gennem <strong>klimaneutralitet, minimering af "
"plastforbruget eller erhvervelse af miljøcertificeringer.</strong> "
"Forbrugere og tilsynsmyndigheder kræver mere miljøvenlige driftsprocesser "
"–<strong>vær foran tidens tendenser</strong> og styrk samtidig dit "
"brandimage og din fortjeneste. Vores skræddersyede strategier gør "
"bæredygtighed <strong>enkelt, praktisk og rentabelt</strong>. Lad os finde "
"ud af, hvordan vi kan hjælpe din virksomhed med at opnå succes og samtidig "
"beskytte planeten."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid "Schedule a demo"
msgstr "Planlæg en demo"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Set up automated <strong>email confirmations and reminders</strong> to "
"ensure clients are notified of their booked demo and any changes."
msgstr ""
"Brug automatiske <strong>e-mail-bekræftelser og påmindelser</strong> til at "
"underrette kunder om demoer og ændringer."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Set up different appointment types (e.g., \"Discovery Call\" and \"Advanced "
"ESG Strategy Demo\") to meet the specific needs of your clients."
msgstr ""
"Opret forskellige typer aftaler "
"(f.eks. \"Første samtale\" og demonstration af en \"Udvidet ESG-strategi\") "
"for at imødekomme dine kunders specifikke behov."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Share a booking link on your website (via the <strong>Website App</strong>) "
"so clients can schedule a demo at their convenience."
msgstr ""
"Del et reservationslink på din hjemmeside via <strong>Hjemmesideappen</"
"strong>, så kunderne selv kan booke en demonstration, når det passer dem."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid "Simplify client engagement with the Appointment App."
msgstr "Gør det lettere at fastholde kunder med Tidsregistreringsappen."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid "Start Acting"
msgstr "Kom i gang"

