msgid ""
"The <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Appointment "
"App</font></strong> allows clients to book demos online."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\""
">Tidsregistreringsappen</font></strong> gør det muligt for kunder at booke "
"demos online."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">CRM "
"App</font></strong> helps you manage client interactions and track potential"
" leads."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">CRM-appen</font></strong> "
"hjælper dig med at håndtere kundeinteraktioner og spore potentielle leads."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Project &amp; "
"Documents App</font></strong> organizes your projects and centralizes key "
"documents."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Projekt- og "
"Dokumenterappen</font></strong> organiserer dine projekter og samler "
"nøgledokumenter."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Sales "
"App</font></strong> streamlines quotations and contract management."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Salgsappen</font></strong> "
"strømliner tilbud og kontrakthåndtering."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Timesheet "
"App</font></strong> tracks time spent on impactful projects and billable "
"hours."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\""
">Tidsregistreringsappen</font></strong>registrerer tiden brugt på vigtige "
"projekter og fakturerbare timer."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Website "
"App</font></strong> showcases your environmental services and expertise."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Hjemmesideappen</font></"
"strong> viser dine miljøtjenester og din ekspertise."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid ""
"The Corporate Sustainability Reporting Directive (CSRD) has been adopted "
"into EU law, making sustainability reporting mandatory for certain "
"companies. Stay ahead by preparing your environmental impact reports now. "
"Contact us to ensure your compliance with ease!"
msgstr ""
"Direktivet om bæredygtighedsrapportering for virksomheder "
"(Corporate Sustainability Reporting Directive, CSRD) er nu indarbejdet i EU-"
"lovgivningen og gør bæredygtighedsrapportering obligatorisk for visse "
"virksomheder. Hold dig opdateret ved at udarbejde dine rapporter om "
"miljøpåvirkninger allerede nu. Kontakt os for at sikre, at du overholder "
"reglerne uden problemer!"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This package is designed to support environmental agencies and consulting "
"firms in optimizing operations, managing projects, and assessing "
"environmental impact with clarity and credibility. Whether conducting carbon"
" footprint analyses, developing sustainability strategies, or guiding "
"organizations in reducing their environmental impact, it enhances overall "
"efficiency and decision-making."
msgstr ""
"Denne pakke er designet til at hjælpe miljømyndigheder og konsulentfirmaer "
"med at optimere deres driftsprocesser, administrere projekter og vurdere "
"miljøpåvirkninger på en klar og troværdig måde. Uanset om det handler om at "
"gennemføre CO₂-fodaftryksanalyser, udvikle bæredygtighedsstrategier eller "
"hjælpe organisationer med at reducere deres miljøpåvirkning, øger pakken den "
"samlede effektivitet og styrker beslutningstagningen."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model:project.task.type,name:environmental_agency.project_task_type_9
msgid "To Do"
msgstr "Gøremål"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid "Track potential clients and manage interactions effectively."
msgstr "Hold styr på leads og interaktioner effektivt."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model:crm.tag,name:environmental_agency.crm_tag_3
msgid "Transport"
msgstr "Transport"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid "Use Case"
msgstr "Brugsscenarie"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use automated follow-ups and plan activities to stay engaged with prospects "
"and improve conversion rates."
msgstr ""
"Brug automatiske opfølgningshandlinger, og planlæg aktiviteter for at bevare "
"kontakten med potentielle medlemmer og øge konverteringsraterne."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use reporting to analyse time spent on different service categories (e.g., "
"strategy consulting, carbon footprint calculations)."
msgstr ""
"Brug rapporteringen til at analysere den tid, der anvendes på forskellige "
"servicekategorier (f.eks. strategisk rådgivning eller beregning af CO₂-"
"aftryk)."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the<strong> timer functionality </strong>to track time spent on a "
"specific client case."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong>Timeren</strong> til at registrere den tid, du har brugt på et "
"bestemt kundesag."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid ""
"We actively engage with our community to promote environmental awareness and"
" participate in local green initiatives, fostering a collective effort "
"toward a more sustainable future."
msgstr ""
"Vi engagerer os aktivt i samfundet for at fremme miljøbevidsthed og deltage "
"i lokale miljøinitiativer, så vi sammen kan skabe en mere bæredygtig fremtid."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3082
msgid ""
"We are a team of passionate people whose goal is to improve everyone's life "
"through disruptive products. We build great products to solve your business "
"problems. Our products are designed for small to medium size companies "
"willing to optimize their performance."
msgstr ""
"Vi er et team af passionerede mennesker, der stræber efter at forbedre alles "
"liv med nyskabende produkter. Vi skaber løsninger, der hjælper dig med at "
"løse dine forretningsudfordringer. Vores produkter er designet til små og "
"mellemstore virksomheder, der ønsker at optimere deres ydeevne."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid ""
"We develop tailored strategies and solutions to address your unique "
"environmental challenges and goals, promoting sustainability and impact."
msgstr ""
"Vi udvikler skræddersyede strategier og løsninger til at håndtere dine "
"specifikke miljømæssige udfordringer og mål, så du kan fremme både "
"bæredygtighed og effektivitet."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid ""
"We implement sustainable practices across all aspects of our operations, "
"from reducing waste and conserving resources to supporting eco-friendly "
"initiatives."
msgstr ""
"Vi anvender bæredygtige metoder i alle dele af vores virksomhed, fra "
"forebyggelse af affald og besparelse af ressourcer til støtte af "
"miljøvenlige initiativer."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.ir_ui_view_3007
msgid ""
"We prioritize energy efficiency in our operations, adopting practices and "
"technologies that reduce energy consumption and lower our carbon footprint."
msgstr ""
"Vi prioriterer energieffektivitet i vores virksomhed ved at anvende metoder "
"og teknologier, der reducerer energiforbruget og mindsker vores økologiske "
"fodaftryk."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid "Welcome to the <strong>Odoo Environmental Agency Package</strong>!"
msgstr "Velkommen til <strong>Odoo-pakken til miljøagenturer</strong>!"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With this module, you can manage opportunities, structure sustainability "
"projects, track consultancy hours, and organize key reports. Features like "
"CRM, Project, and Timesheet simplify daily tasks, while Appointment allows "
"clients to book demos with ease."
msgstr ""
"Med dette modul kan du administrere salgsmuligheder, strukturere "
"bæredygtighedsprojekter, følge op på konsultationstimer og organisere "
"vigtige rapporter. Funktioner som CRM, projekter og tidsregistrering "
"forenkler de daglige opgaver, mens aftaleplanlægning gør det nemt for "
"kunderne at booke demoer."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"Vil du gerne tale med os om dit Odoo-setup eller drøfte nogle spørgsmål mere "
"detaljeret?"

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilgå alle installerede apps i din Odoo-database direkte fra "
"hoveddashboardet."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"Du har nu gennemført demoens brugsscenarie. Odoo kan tilpasses på utallige "
"måder, så løsningen matcher netop din virksomheds behov."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries"
" &gt; Upgrade your Environmental Agency package and check the related box."
msgstr ""
"Har du ikke importeret demodata endnu? Du kan stadig nå det. Gå til Apps &gt;"
" Brancher &gt; Opgradér din pakke til miljøagenturer, og markér det "
"relevante felt."

#. module: environmental_agency
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:environmental_agency.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Du bør kunne gennemføre følgende flows for at få et overblik over de "
"forskellige processer, som du hurtigt kan udføre med denne pakke i Odoo."

